# Simple Calculator in Python
This is a simple calculator program written in Phyton.
It can perform basic arithmetic operations.
# Features 
- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division
- Continuous mode(run multiple times)
- Exit option
 # Texnologies
 Phyton 3
 # How to run
 1. Make sure Phyton is installed on your system
 2. Clone this to repository or download the file
 3. Run the program using :
ʼʼʼbash
phyton calculator.py

